Name: Jinzhou Stew
Desc: Increases all team members' ATK by 8% and Crit. Rate by 6%, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
Bg: A stew comprised of mixed protein and vegetables. The popular Jinzhou family meal allows for the preservation of the ingredients' natural flavors to the maximum owing to its simplicity and versatility. "Jinzhou Stew, Jingzhou brew!"
